These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
Food: strawberry, broccoli, lemon, papaya
1. Food:strawberry is on the far left##1
2. Food:broccoli is on the left or right of Food:strawberry##3
3. Food:broccoli is on the left or right of Food:lemon##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | strawberry | broccoli | lemon | papaya |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
Beverage: cola, milk, almond-milk, tea
1. Beverage:cola is on the right of Beverage:milk##1
2. Beverage:tea is on the left of Beverage:almond-milk##1
3. Beverage:almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk | cola | tea | almond-milk |

 #################################
 
